page_title: What's new in Azure OpenAI Service?
page_description: Learn about the latest news and features updates for Azure OpenAI.
chunk_content: January 2023### New Features* Service GA. Azure OpenAI Service is now generally available.​* New models: Addition of the latest text model, text-davinci-003 (East US, West Europe), text-ada-embeddings-002 (East US, South Central US, West Europe)
